### 1️⃣ Record a New Chain Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "TransferRecorded",
  "entity_type": "batch",
  "entity_id": "af7df286-383c-44d1-8132-5f523c3e1cbe",
  "details": {
    "from_actor": "Farmer Ajith",
    "to_actor": "FPO-07",
    "quantity_kg": 120,
    "location_name": "Village Collection Center"
  },
  "tx_hash": "0xabc123..."
}

### 2️⃣ Fetch All Chain Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events

### 3️⃣ Fetch Events by Entity
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events/entity/batch/af7df286-383c-44d1-8132-5f523c3e1cbe

### 4️⃣ Fetch Events by Actor
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events/actor/FPO-07

### 5️⃣ Fetch Latest Event for an Entity
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events/latest/batch/af7df286-383c-44d1-8132-5f523c3e1cbe

### 6️⃣ Verify Event on Blockchain
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chain-events/10039332-07a3-4b1e-8447-2a14c69056ab/verify
